{"tid":1790772,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[冷靜思考] 希望唔好重演poly 果時，被警曱捉晒勇武","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T09:12:15.000Z","uid":61520,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b43b8382be258c127ac3d163dab687f62305688","tid":1790772,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"大家諗下點解我地會靜左咁耐， 就係poly 果次被情緒影響， 結果兩日無左兩千幾兩千個手足。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁係咪唔勇武？？ NO !!!<br />\n但真係唔好打陣地，唔理你裝修紅商又好，神獸警曱又好。 要快閃。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">女手足 幾嬲都好，發夢前問自己，你體能得唔得？ 最底限度自問可唔可以跑到10km, 唔得幾練好體能前做和理非 backup 前線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">和理非 出得去唔該勇少少， 見到手足俾人捉既話 我地人多時要救佢地<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地既target 係經濟攬炒佢， 而手足盡量唔好被捉，咁先可以鬥長命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e4b19f294b1b3dc383aa9e32c9115d58a9ddb4e","tid":1790772,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5SHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=22bde92b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5SHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=1702c1e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: